txt.en: You have a fixed amount of time in which to drink as much as Damkalb, the current drinking champion of the Corsairs under Jajax.
'Are you ready? Drink fast, if you can. We count as soon as you accept this challenge. If you fail, things may not go well for you....'
Drinks can be found in the tavern of Lothgobel in central Lamedon.\n\nYou should drink quickly to best the drinking champion of Jajax's Corsairs.
